com.facebook.buck.rules

Class BuildResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.rules.BuildResult

  • public class BuildResult
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a union type that represents either a success or a failure. This exists so that com.facebook.buck.rules.CachingBuildEngine#buildOnceDepsAreBuilt() can return a strongly typed value.
